Day 1 of React:
  What is react?
->Reactjs is a declarative, efficient and flexible javascript library for building reusable UI components. It is an open source, component based front end library which is responsible only for the view layer of the application. It was initally developed and maintained by Facebook.

  Why use reactJS?
-> The main objective of ReactJS is to develop User Interface(UI) that improves the speed of the apps. It uses virtual DOM(Javascript object) which impproves the performance of the app. 

